  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eAs an expert vintner would transform humble grapes into extraordinary wine, \u003ca href=\"https://naturehumaine.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e_naturehumaine’s\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e latest architectural work, \u003ca href=\"https://naturehumaine.com/portfolio/le-petit-merlot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLe Petit Merlot\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, converts a classic 1920s duplex into a contemporary haven. Nestled in the gastronomic heart of Montreal’s Plateau Mont-Royal, this thoughtful renovation embodies the same patient craftsmanship as its namesake – a careful fermentation of old and new, where historical elements are preserved and enhanced through time.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561875\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561875\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-17-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with large windows, white cabinets, and a central island with a stool. Glass table in the foreground and view of a wooden fence outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-17-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-17-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-17-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSited on a compact lot without an alley, the duplex adjoins two neighboring homes and aligns with the shared front street boundary. It includes two stacked units, accessible through a rear courtyard via a porte-cochère. Restricted to two floors, the design adds a mezzanine level, extending the space for the upper unit without exceeding height limits. Heritage features were restored for the front facade, with the original red clay brick, painted hemlock lintels, and stone spandrels retained for architectural authenticity. French windows with divided panes and restored wooden cornices reflect the area’s historical facades, contributing to a cohesive street presence.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561876\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561876\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-16-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with white cabinets, a beige tiled backsplash, and a gray island countertop. A coffee machine is on the counter.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-16-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-16-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-16-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-16-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561885\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561885\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-3-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with gray cabinets, an island with a sink, and a stool. Adjacent is a dining table with chairs. Large red-framed windows allow natural light to fill the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-3-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-3-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-3.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInside, the lower 1,420-square-foot unit is designed to harmonize with the garden. A glass rear facade blurs the line between indoor and outdoor spaces, opening the living area, dining room, kitchen, and bedroom to the landscape. Below, a sunken courtyard introduces light to the basement-level office and additional bedroom. The upper unit prioritizes southern natural light, with a mezzanine housing the kitchen and dining area, leading to a wooden terrace featuring steel planters. A central staircase, clad in white perforated steel, visually connects the levels.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561884\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561884\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-4-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with white cabinets, beige tile backsplash, and a stainless steel sink. A window provides natural light. A yellow pot with a potted plant sits on the countertop.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-4-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-4-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-4-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-4-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561874\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561874\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-19-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern dining area with a glass table, wooden chairs, a unique chandelier, and large red-framed windows overlooking a wooden fence and brick wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-19-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-19-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-19-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-19-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561883\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561883\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-6-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden cabinet and chair beneath a staircase with a mesh screen. A small plant, books, and a clock sit atop the cabinet.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-6-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-6-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-6-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-6-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn contrast to the heritage front, the rear facade takes a modern approach. Large glass sections span four levels between brick walls, lending the interior a soft, ambient light. To enhance the basement unit’s light quality, floor-to-ceiling windows create a spacious feel in the bedroom and office. Interior finishes echo the exterior’s red tones in materials and paint, maintaining visual unity. This color scheme is evident in brick, window mullions, steel accents, and select indoor elements like the library and lighting fixtures.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561881\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561881\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-9-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior with wooden floors, white walls, and large frosted glass panel. A corridor leads to a room with a wooden chair and a large window providing natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-9-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-9-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561882\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561882\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-8-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A modern interior features a wooden chair by a large window overlooking greenery. Fluted glass partition and wooden furniture are visible in the foreground.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/202