080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-11-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-11-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-11-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561873\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561873\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-21-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A bedroom with a wooden bed, white curtains, and an open door leading to a garden with plants.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-21-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-21-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-21-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561878\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561878\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-12-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist bathroom with a gray countertop, sink, and mirrored cabinets. Two windows with wooden frames let in natural light. Small potted plants are on the windowsills.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-12-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/naturehumaine-lepetitmerlot-12-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/n